g 32 years, from 1979 to 2011.\n\nSince 15 June 2019, the city mayor is Ana Gonz\u00e1lez Rodr\u00edguez of [[Spanish Socialist Workers' Party|PSOE]].\n\n===Councillors distribution in local elections===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size:97%;\"\n|- bgcolor=\"#CCCCCC\"\n! colspan=\"3\" |Councilors for Gij\u00f3n since 1979\n|-\n| colspan=\"3\" |\n{| class=\"navbox collapsible collapsed\" style=\"text-align:left; font-size:100%; width:100%; float:left; border:0; margin-top:-1px;\"\n|-\n! colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:#FDFDFD;\"| ''Key to parties''\n|-\n| style=\"font-size:95%; border:solid 1px silver; padding:8px; background:white;\"|\n{{div col|colwidth=12.5em}}\n{{legend|{{Xix\u00f3n S\u00ed Puede/meta/color}}|{{Tooltip|XSP|Xix\u00f3n S\u00ed Puede}}|border=1px solid #AAAAAA}}\n{{legend|{{Podemos Asturias/meta/color}}|[[Podemos Asturias|Podemos]]|border=1px solid #AAAAAA}}\n{{legend|{{Communist Party of Asturias/meta/color}}|[[Communist Party of Asturias|PCA\u2013PCE]]|border=1px solid #AAAAAA}}\n{{legend|{{United Left of Asturias/meta/color}}|[[United Left of Asturias|IU\u2013IX]]|border=1px solid #AAAAAA}}\n{{legend|{{Asturian Socialist Federation/meta/color}}|[[Asturian Socialist Federation|PSOE]]|border=1px solid #AAAAAA}}\n{{legend|{{Gijonese Unity/meta/color}}|{{Tooltip|UGJ|Gijonese Unity}}|border=1px solid #AAAAAA}}\n{{legend|{{Union of the Democratic Centre (Spain)/meta/color}}|[[Union of the Democratic Centre (Spain)|UCD]]|border=1px solid #AAAAAA}}\n{{legend|{{Citizens (Spanish political party)/meta/color}}|[[Citizens (Spanish political party)|Cs]]|border=1px solid #AAAAAA}}\n{{legend|{{Democratic and Social Centre (Spain)/meta/color}}|[[Democratic and Social Centre (Spain)|CDS]]|border=1px solid #AAAAAA}}\n{{legend|{{Democratic Coalition (Spain)/meta/color}}|[[Democratic Coalition (Spain)|CD]]|border=1px solid #AAAAAA}}\n{{legend|{{Asturias Forum/meta/color}}|[[Asturias Forum|FAC]]|border=1px solid #AAAAAA}}\n{{legend|{{People's Party of Asturias/meta/color}}|[[People's Party of Asturias|PP]]|border=1px solid #AAAAAA}}\n{{legend|{{People's Coalition (Spain)/meta/color}}|[[People's Coalition (Spain)|CP]]|border=1px solid #AAAAAA}}\n{{legend|{{People's Alliance (Spain)/meta/color}}|[[People's Alliance (Spain)|AP]]|border=1px solid #AAAAAA}}\n{{legend|{{Vox (political party)/meta/color}}|[[Vox (political party)|Vox]]|border=1px solid #AAAAAA}}\n{{colend}}\n|}\n|- bgcolor=\"#CCCCCC\"\n! Election\n! Distribution\n!Mayor\n|-\n| align=center|[[Results breakdown of the 1979 Spanish local elections (Asturias)#Gij\u00f3n|1979]]\n|\n{| style=\"width:45em; font-size:85%; text-align:center; font-family:Courier New;\"\n|- style=\"font-weight:bold\"\n| style=\"background:{{Communist Party of Asturias/meta/color}}; width:14.81%; color:white;\"| 4\n| style=\"background:{{Asturian Socialist Federation/meta/color}}; width:48.14%; color:white;\"| 13\n| style=\"background:{{Union of the Democratic Centre (Spain)/meta/color}}; width:33.33%; color:white;\"| 9\n| style=\"background:{{Democratic Coalition (Spain)/meta/color}}; width:3.7%; color:white;\"| 1\n|}\n|Jos\u00e9 Manuel Palacio ([[Asturian Socialist Federation|PSOE]])\n|-\n| align=center|[[Results breakdown of the 1983 Spanish local elections (Asturias)#Gij\u00f3n|1983]]\n|\n{| style=\"width:45em; font-size:85%; text-align:center; font-family:Courier New;\"\n|- style=\"font-weight:bold\"\n| style=\"background:{{Communist Party of Asturias/meta/color}}; width:11.11%; color:white;\"| 3\n| style=\"background:{{Asturian Socialist Federation/meta/color}}; width:62.96%; color:white;\"| 17\n| style=\"background:{{People's Coalition (Spain)/meta/color}}; width:25.93%; color:white;\"| 7\n|}\n| rowspan=\"4\" |[[Vicente \u00c1lvarez Areces]] ([[Asturian Socialist Federation|PSOE]])\n|-\n| align=center|[[Results breakdown of the 1987 Spanish local elections (Asturias)#Gij\u00f3n|1987]]\n|\n{| style=\"width:45em; font-size:85%; text-align:center; font-family:Courier New;\"\n|- style=