bach]]\n|Danish\n|\"[[Disco Tango]]\"\n|align=center|6\n|align=center|76\n|-\n!{{Escyr|1980}}\n|[[Bamses Venner]]\n|Danish\n|\"[[T\u00e6nker altid p\u00e5 dig]]\"\n|align=center|14 \n|align=center|25\n|-\n!{{Escyr|1981}}\n|[[Tommy Seebach]] and [[Debbie Cameron]]\n|Danish\n|\"[[Kr\u00f8ller eller ej]]\"\n|align=center|11\n|align=center|41\n|-\n!{{Escyr|1982}}\n|[[Brixx]]\n|Danish\n|\"[[Video, Video]]\"\n|align=center|17\n|align=center|5\n|-\n!{{Escyr|1983}}\n|[[Gry Johansen]]\n|Danish\n|\"[[Kloden drejer]]\"\n|align=center|17\n|align=center|16\n|-\n!{{Escyr|1984}}\n|[[Hot Eyes]]\n|Danish\n|\"[[Det' lige det]]\"\n|align=center|4\n|align=center|101\n|-\n!{{Escyr|1985}}\n|[[Hot Eyes]]\n|Danish\n|\"[[Sku' du sp\u00f8rg' fra no'en?]]\"\n|align=center|11 \n|align=center|41\n|-\n!{{Escyr|1986}}\n|[[Lise Haavik]]\n|Danish\n|\"[[Du er fuld af l\u00f8gn]]\"\n|align=center|6\n|align=center|77\n|-\n!{{Escyr|1987}}\n|[[Anne-Cathrine Herdorf]]\n|Danish\n|\"[[En lille melodi]]\"\n|align=center|5\n|align=center|83\n|-bgcolor=\"#C96\" \n!{{Escyr|1988}}\n|[[Hot Eyes]]\n|Danish\n|\"[[Ka' du se hva' jeg sa'?]]\"\n|align=center|3 \n|align=center|92\n|-bgcolor=\"#C96\" \n!{{Escyr|1989}}\n|[[Birthe Kj\u00e6r]]\n|Danish\n|\"[[Vi maler byen r\u00f8d]]\"\n|align=center|3\n|align=center|111\n|-\n!{{Escyr|1990}}\n|[[Lonnie Devantier]]\n|Danish\n|\"[[Hallo Hallo (Lonnie Devantier song)|Hallo Hallo]]\"\n|align=center|8\n|align=center|64\n|-\n!{{Escyr|1991}}\n|[[Anders Frandsen]]\n|Danish\n|\"[[Lige der hvor hjertet sl\u00e5r]]\"\n|align=center|19\n|align=center|8\n|-\n!{{Escyr|1992}}\n|[[Lotte Feder]] and [[Kenny L\u00fcbcke]]\n|Danish\n|\"[[Alt det som ingen ser]]\"\n|align=center|12\n|align=center|47\n|-\n!{{Escyr|1993}}\n|[[Tommy Seebach|Tommy Seebach Band]]\n|Danish\n|\"[[Under stjernerne p\u00e5 himlen]]\"\n|align=center|22\n|align=center|9\n|colspan=\"2\" data-sort-value=\"-9999\" {{N/A|[[Kvalifikacija za Millstreet]]}}\n|-\n|{{N/A|{{Escyr|1994}}}}\n|colspan=\"7\" {{N/A|Did not participate