uary 2010\n| style=\"width:125px;\"| [[BBC Two]]\n| style=\"width:125px; \"rowspan=\"2\" | 2 March 2020\n| style=\"width:125px;\" |[[BBC One]]\n|-\n| style=\"width:250px;\"| ''[[Liar (TV series)|Liar]]''\n| style=\"width:125px;\"| 16 October 2017\n| style=\"width:125px;\"| ITV\n| style=\"width:125px;\"| N/A (same channel as original)\n|-\n| style=\"width:250px;\"| ''[[Our Girl]]''\n| style=\"width:125px;\"| 24 July 2018\n| style=\"width:125px;\"| BBC One\n| style=\"width:125px;\"| 24 March 2020\n| style=\"width:125px;\"| N/A (same channel as original)\n|-\n| style=\"width:250px;\"| ''[[In My Skin (TV series)|In My Skin]]''\n| style=\"width:125px;\"| 14 October 2018\n| style=\"width:125px;\"| [[BBC Three]]\n| style=\"width:125px;\"| 29 March 2020\n| style=\"width:125px;\"| N/A (same channel as original)\n|-\n| style=\"width:250px;\"| ''[[Ackley Bridge]]''\n| style=\"width:125px;\"| 6 August 2019\n| style=\"width:125px;\"| [[Channel 4]]\n| style=\"width:125px;\"| TBA<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.halifaxcourier.co.uk/arts-and-culture/film-and-tv/filming-ackley-bridge-series-four-postponed-amid-coronavirus-2483063%3famp|title=Filming for Ackley Bridge series four postponed amid coronavirus|work=[[Halifax Courier]]|access-date=20 March 2020}}</ref>\n| style=\"width:125px;\"| N/A (same channel as original)\n|-\n| style=\"width:250px;\"| ''[[Spitting Image]]''\n| style=\"width:125px;\"| 18 February 1996\n| style=\"width:125px;\"| ITV\n| style=\"width:125px;\"| TBA<ref name=\"autogenerated1\"/>\n| style=\"width:125px;\"| [[BritBox]]\n|-\n| style=\"width:250px;\"| ''BBC Cricket''\n| style=\"width:125px;\"| 1939<br>1999\n| style=\"width:125px;\"| BBC One<br>BBC Two\n| style=\"width:125px;\"| TBA\n| style=\"width:125px;\"| N/A (same channel as original)\n|}\n\n===1950s===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! width=250|Programme\n! width=250|Date\n|-\n|''[[Panorama (TV series)|Panorama]]''\n|(1953\u2013present)\n|-\n|''[[The Sky at Night]]''\n|(1957\u2013present)\n|-\n|''[[Final S